s="t m3f x6d hb y374 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m325 x92 hb y374 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m32c x6b hb y375 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Job 31:38-40 </div><div class="t m3f x6d hb y376 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m325 x92 hb y376 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m54 x4b hb y377 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How would you explain to someone the necessity of the exist-</div><div class="t m32d x43 hb y378 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ence of the law before Sinai? If, as John (1 John 3:4) wrote, </div><div class="t m8d x43 hb y379 ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Whosoever committeth sin transgresseth also the law: for sin is </div><div class="t m32e x43 hb y37a ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the transgression of the law,&quot; why did the law have to predate </div><div class="t m32f x43 hb y37b ff4 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Sinai? </div><div class="t m232 x4a hf y37c ff2 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">25 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
